Dear Raesibje Listar Mthombeni,



We would like to officially welcome you to the iRam team and congratulate y=
ou on being selected for the role of Casual/General Merchandiser - start da=
te 24 June 2026.

Please read through the below carefully as well as the attached, should you=
 have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us directly. Please a=
lso see the attached Handbook and familiarize yourself with the policies an=
d procedures of the company. Included as well are The Five Fundamentals and=
 Confidential rules which should be enforced and upheld at all times.

Employee information - Important to be completed.

The below two links MUST be completed ASAP. Failure to complete the iRam Em=
ployee Take on Form could result in you not being paid on time due to being=
 unable to load you onto our payroll.

1.      iRam Employee Take On Form : https://www.cognitoforms.com/IRam1/Emp=
loyeeTakeOnFormFNL
2.      iRam In Case of Emergency Form: https://www.cognitoforms.com/IRam1/=
iramincaseofemergencyform

Please note that you will be required to sign a copy of your contract.

It will be sent to you via an electronic platform for signing - Quickly Sig=
n.

Once received - please ensure that you sign where indicated on the respecti=
ve pages.

We wish you all the best in your new role!









Kind Regards,



iRam HR Team



